1
00:01:25,390 --> 00:01:29,960
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:33,930
[Episode 38]

3
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:42,680
Attack!

4
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:45,789
Attack!

5
00:02:04,810 --> 00:02:05,530
It's me,

6
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,680
Yan Ze,

7
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:12,510
an orphan whose parents
both died because of you.

8
00:02:12,510 --> 00:02:13,720
How did you know?

9
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:18,320
It must be you wretched lackey.

10
00:02:19,110 --> 00:02:19,670
I...

11
00:02:20,410 --> 00:02:22,340
I trusted and valued you so deeply,

12
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:24,680
yet you dared to collude with traitors

13
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:25,829
and betray me!

14
00:02:26,230 --> 00:02:27,040
As they say,

15
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:30,670
evil deeds will eventually
lead to self-destruction.

16
00:02:30,670 --> 00:02:31,390
Yuan Qing,

17
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,850
serve tea to the sinner.

18
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,110
Yuan Qing...

19
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,450
Your Majesty, don't worry.

20
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:51,610
I've added the same amount of
Dream Butterfly Poison to this tea

21
00:02:51,610 --> 00:02:54,329
as was given to the late Princess Xin.

22
00:02:54,950 --> 00:02:57,480
Your Majesty will have plenty of time
to savor

23
00:02:57,550 --> 00:02:58,600
and watch,

24
00:02:58,829 --> 00:03:01,790
to see clearly
how the late Princess Xin died!

25
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:07,600
The Dream Butterfly Poison you found
back then was made from the wing powder

26
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:10,880
of the Five-colored Butterfly
from the Southern Frontier.

27
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,280
This poison is colorless and odorless,

28
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:14,110
only detectable after it takes effect.

29
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:15,280
My poor mother.

30
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,790
She saved your life,

31
00:03:18,350 --> 00:03:20,990
yet became the first person you used
to test poison.

32
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:23,720
Poor me. I tested the water temperature
for my dying mother,

33
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:26,180
yet got my eyesight ruined
with just one sip!

34
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:31,130
My Father followed my mother in death,

35
00:03:32,230 --> 00:03:34,040
surely also your doing.

36
00:03:35,950 --> 00:03:37,510
This is

37
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,829
as heartless as it gets.

38
00:03:40,829 --> 00:03:42,230
Don't you

39
00:03:42,950 --> 00:03:44,440
celebrate too soon.

40
00:03:45,150 --> 00:03:45,870
I

41
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:50,390
still have two palace guard divisions
standing by on full alert,

42
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:52,760
as well as the Huaiyang Army,

43
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:54,410
which will soon

44
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:57,040
enter the capital to protect me.

45
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:02,079
Has Your Majesty forgotten?

46
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:05,070
The one who delivered your verbal orders
to the Palace Guard Division

47
00:04:05,070 --> 00:04:06,280
was me.

48
00:04:06,790 --> 00:04:08,920
You won't be seeing the Huaiyang Army.

49
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:09,550
You...

50
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,280
You...

51
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:11,200
You...

52
00:04:11,670 --> 00:04:13,230
You bastard!

53
00:04:13,230 --> 00:04:14,600
I'll kill you!

54
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:16,550
Traitor Yan Han,

55
00:04:17,280 --> 00:04:19,140
such an end for you is only proper,

56
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,279
showing that justice prevails!

57
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:26,839
Yuan Qing!

58
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,650
Read the Self-reproach Edict.

59
00:04:41,110 --> 00:04:41,670
Yan?

60
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,440
-Li.
-What are you doing?

61
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,120
Why are you here?

62
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:51,440
You've come at the perfect time.

63
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,500
A son pays for his father's debts—

64
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,840
that is the eternal way of heaven.

65
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:57,550
You...

66
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:58,600
Li.

67
00:04:58,990 --> 00:05:00,159
Li, leave now!

68
00:05:00,159 --> 00:05:00,920
They...

69
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,640
They're all rebels!

70
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:04,840
Hurry, Li.

71
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,190
Li!

72
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:07,040
Li!

73
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,150
Yan Ze!

74
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,400
Yan Ze,

75
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,250
what are you doing?

76
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,990
Li! Li!

77
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,830
Yan Ze, you've gone crazy!

78
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:20,960
What exactly are you trying to do?

79
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:21,640
Yan Li.

80
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:25,350
Listen carefully to
that Self-reproach Edict

81
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:28,440
and see the true colors of
this emperor before you.

82
00:05:29,790 --> 00:05:30,520
Yuan Qing!

83
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,430
Yuan Qing!

84
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:36,160
By Heaven's mandate, I issue
this edict of self-reproach to the world.

85
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:36,640
I,

86
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,920
Yan Han, the second legitimate son
of the late Emperor,

87
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:41,480
incited Fu Chengye to rebel,

88
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,750
attempting to seize the throne,

89
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:45,840
-pretended to surrender
-Yuan Qing!

90
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:47,080
to lure my twin brother
Yan Huai to Storm Ridge

91
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,430
for a private meeting,

92
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:50,159
where I murdered him

93
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,870
and destroyed all evidence, after which

94
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:54,990
-I took the throne in my brother's name.
-What wrong did I do? I'm innocent!

95
00:05:54,990 --> 00:05:57,159
-From then on, the order was overturned,
-I'm the chosen one!

96
00:05:57,159 --> 00:06:00,020
the sun and moon darkened,
and all conscience lost.

97
00:06:00,110 --> 00:06:01,400
End of the decree.

98
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:11,340
How dare you, a usurper of the throne,

99
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,990
claim you're the chosen one?

100
00:06:14,230 --> 00:06:15,690
These are all just ravings

101
00:06:16,350 --> 00:06:17,150
and nonsense.

102
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:18,890
Whether it's nonsense or not,

103
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:21,040
he himself knows best.

104
00:06:21,860 --> 00:06:22,980
Isn't that right,

105
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:23,920
Prince Yi?

106
00:06:25,550 --> 00:06:26,190
You...

107
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:27,600
You...

108
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:29,020
Prince Yi?

109
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:30,290
You heard it right.

110
00:06:31,690 --> 00:06:33,460
He is your biological father,

111
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,350
Prince Yi, Yan Han.

112
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,340
My dear son, Li.

113
00:06:47,550 --> 00:06:48,750
My dear son, Li!

114
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:51,760
Li.

115
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,280
Father...

116
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,110
Li.

117
00:06:56,230 --> 00:06:57,200
Li.

118
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,040
Impossible.

119
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,210
This is impossible.

120
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,610
Otherwise, why do you think he allowed

121
00:07:03,650 --> 00:07:07,170
Prince Cheng and the Crown Prince
to turn against each other,

122
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:10,010
yet treated you better than his own sons?

123
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:15,400
So what if I am Yan Han?

124
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:16,290
I

125
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:19,080
am also the Empress Dowager's
biological son,

126
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:21,960
still of the royal bloodline.

127
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:23,310
Just because

128
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:26,110
I was a twin,

129
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,600
the Yan family

130
00:07:28,230 --> 00:07:30,600
cast me aside like worn-out shoes!

131
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:33,280
Who has ever sought justice for me?

132
00:07:33,790 --> 00:07:35,320
Heaven's justice is clear.

133
00:07:35,620 --> 00:07:36,600
What the Yan family

134
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,750
owed me

135
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:40,210
should naturally be repaid
with the throne!

136
00:07:40,350 --> 00:07:42,480
I have no shame before Heaven and Earth,

137
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,890
nor before my parents!

138
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:53,930
What about me and my mother?

139
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,409
Do you also feel no guilt toward us?

140
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:20,480
Li.

141
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:23,450
Why don't you ask your biological father

142
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:26,140
how Chi's mother died,

143
00:08:27,050 --> 00:08:27,910
how Consort Jin

144
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,520
met her end,

145
00:08:30,110 --> 00:08:31,720
and what caused

146
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,200
Prince Jin and Shen Yi's deaths?

147
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:41,789
No way...

148
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,240
Li.

149
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,840
Everything I've done

150
00:08:46,669 --> 00:08:48,710
is for you.

151
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:53,830
I didn't want you to suffer

152
00:08:54,590 --> 00:08:56,250
a life of hardships like I did!

153
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:57,920
Li.

154
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,280
I did it all for you,

155
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:03,070
clearing away all obstacles,

156
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:08,090
just so you could ascend to the throne!

157
00:09:09,350 --> 00:09:10,110
No.

158
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:12,280
This can't be true.

159
00:09:12,310 --> 00:09:13,450
Li!

160
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,590
No!

161
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,340
This can't be true!

162
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:33,710
Yan Li.

163
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,640
My dear Li!

164
00:09:35,860 --> 00:09:37,250
You wretched lackey!

165
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:38,720
You... You...

166
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,140
I'll kill you!

167
00:09:45,470 --> 00:09:46,160
Yan Han.

168
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:49,950
Even your own son,

169
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:52,430
whom you have such high hopes for,
doesn't believe your lies.

170
00:09:52,430 --> 00:09:55,160
When you abandoned your wife and child
back then,

171
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,360
did you ever think it would come to this?

172
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,040
You...

173
00:10:09,430 --> 00:10:10,000
Yan Ze.

174
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:13,470
Yan Ze.

175
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,070
Yan Ze!

176
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:16,640
Yan Ze!

177
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,160
Li, wake up!

178
00:10:18,180 --> 00:10:19,300
Li, wake up!

179
00:10:19,330 --> 00:10:22,450
Li, wake up!

180
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,430
To use your son's blood

181
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:55,840
to complete this unrighteous flower
and send you to your death—

182
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,830
I suppose it can be considered

183
00:11:57,830 --> 00:12:00,290
me granting a final favor
to you and your son.

184
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,470
Body sacrifice,

185
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,470
heavens tremble,

186
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:09,990
with flying dragons' protection,

187
00:12:09,990 --> 00:12:11,720
immortal and indestructible!

188
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:14,410
Spare...

189
00:12:14,430 --> 00:12:15,550
Spare Li.

190
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:18,620
I will immediately draft a decree

191
00:12:19,470 --> 00:12:20,240
to

192
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:23,790
pass the throne to you.

193
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:26,360
Yuan Qing,

194
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:28,190
tell me,

195
00:12:28,470 --> 00:12:29,920
should I take the throne?

196
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:32,400
Leader, your virtue shines bright

197
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,640
and your noble spirit reaches far.

198
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:36,370
You are the heaven-ordained sovereign
of the...

199
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:46,830
You lied to me...

200
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:53,590
You're all...

201
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,390
The same...

202
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,190
You're right.

203
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:11,220
Sooner or later, you'll be

204
00:13:11,740 --> 00:13:14,470
discarded like a tool
that's served its purpose.

205
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,200
I only want the throne

206
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:22,080
so that everyone who enabled Yan Han

207
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,160
will pay for my parents' deaths.

208
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:29,280
You've helped me achieve my goal.

209
00:13:30,730 --> 00:13:31,900
Rest in peace now.

210
00:13:36,470 --> 00:13:37,670
How cruel is fate,

211
00:13:39,130 --> 00:13:40,530
so many die with regrets.

212
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,560
May he in his next life

213
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:46,160
never again believe in

214
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:47,960
carrying out heaven's justice.

215
00:14:58,430 --> 00:14:58,960
Let's go!

216
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:01,190
Bai Feng!

217
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,220
Hurry up and go!

218
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:16,240
Let's go!

219
00:15:22,430 --> 00:15:24,520
The ringleader of
the Heavenly Way Society,

220
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:26,320
Yuan Qing, has been eliminated.

221
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:27,400
After today,

222
00:15:28,170 --> 00:15:31,640
no one will know about my connection
to the Heavenly Way Society.

223
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:33,370
People will only remember that

224
00:15:33,570 --> 00:15:36,240
you died at the hands of  Yuan Qing,
the traitor from the Heavenly Way Society,

225
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,240
and that Yuan Qing

226
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,260
and your precious son killed each other.

227
00:15:40,550 --> 00:15:42,790
Except for your crimes
that will be made public,

228
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:43,960
all the truth

229
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:46,400
will vanish into thin air.

230
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:54,240
Li!

231
00:15:56,070 --> 00:15:57,000
Are you alright?

232
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,050
Are you alright?

233
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:00,480
Are you alright?

234
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,080
I never thought

235
00:16:07,190 --> 00:16:08,920
that I, Yan Li, would end up

236
00:16:09,670 --> 00:16:11,640
dying alongside you.

237
00:16:14,310 --> 00:16:16,240
I wonder if I'll ever

238
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:19,190
have a chance to see Ning again.

239
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:22,160
If she sees me like this,

240
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:24,640
she'll surely be disgusted.

241
00:16:24,780 --> 00:16:26,380
I'm here with you, Li.

242
00:16:30,670 --> 00:16:31,310
Good.

243
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:34,280
I'll let you fully experience

244
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:38,430
what it feels like to watch
your loved ones die right before your eyes

245
00:16:38,430 --> 00:16:40,190
and be powerless to save them—

246
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:43,700
that heart-wrenching, gut-twisting pain.

247
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:51,880
Li!

248
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,000
Wan.

249
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:08,070
How is

250
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:09,270
Li?

251
00:17:09,630 --> 00:17:10,510
I can save him.

252
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,990
You liar! Murderer!

253
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:52,270
Young Marshal,
hurry and go protect His Majesty!

254
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:53,400
Leave this to us!

255
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:54,840
Master.

256
00:17:55,260 --> 00:17:56,060
How is Sui?

257
00:17:56,230 --> 00:17:56,990
He's all right,

258
00:17:56,990 --> 00:17:58,120
probably just choked a bit.

259
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:58,880
Someone set a fire inside.

260
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,000
I've already put it out.

261
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,790
Princess Wan and Yongning
are already in the bedchamber.

262
00:18:02,790 --> 00:18:03,750
Take good care of Sui.

263
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:04,470
I'll go save Princess Wan.

264
00:18:04,470 --> 00:18:04,920
Yes.

265
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:27,870
Yan Li!

266
00:18:32,190 --> 00:18:33,120
Chi.

267
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:34,840
He's not the Cousin Yan we knew anymore.

268
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:35,900
He wants to kill us!

269
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:38,800
Chi.

270
00:18:40,030 --> 00:18:40,760
My father...

271
00:18:41,150 --> 00:18:42,430
He killed His Majesty

272
00:18:43,270 --> 00:18:44,320
and your mother.

273
00:18:45,080 --> 00:18:45,840
And also...

274
00:18:46,840 --> 00:18:47,880
For these sins,

275
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:49,830
let me pay with my life.

276
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:52,550
You and he are different people.

277
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:53,980
You must live on.

278
00:18:58,120 --> 00:18:58,640
Master!

279
00:18:58,950 --> 00:19:00,190
The rebels are retreating.

280
00:19:00,190 --> 00:19:01,590
Take them all out of here.

281
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:03,140
-Yes!
-Be careful.

282
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:07,270
Here.

283
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:10,710
Don't worry about me.

284
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:13,060
Take Li away.

285
00:19:13,600 --> 00:19:15,430
Take Li away first.

286
00:19:36,120 --> 00:19:36,640
Here.

287
00:19:57,320 --> 00:19:58,080
Chi.

288
00:19:59,030 --> 00:20:00,710
Yan Han killed our parents.

