never showing any suspicion.

571
00:38:04,720 --> 00:38:05,550
I don't like

572
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,680
hearing such talk.

573
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:09,630
What do you mean by "using connections"?

574
00:38:09,630 --> 00:38:11,240
Using connections means taking advantage

575
00:38:11,240 --> 00:38:13,400
of others for personal gain.

576
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:15,130
You rely on your own abilities,

577
00:38:15,340 --> 00:38:16,940
and you're so kind-hearted.

578
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:19,180
That's why I love and cherish you.

579
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:22,060
This is the bond between us.

580
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:26,590
Whether you're Qin Wan or Shen Wan,

581
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:28,470
you will always be

582
00:38:29,280 --> 00:38:31,240
my most beloved granddaughter.

583
00:38:33,160 --> 00:38:37,960
♪ A deep mark you left,
etched in my heart ♪

584
00:38:37,110 --> 00:38:37,920
Grandma.

585
00:38:40,450 --> 00:38:44,780
♪ Now and then it aches,
stirring old memories ♪

586
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:44,860
Alright, alright.

587
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:48,450
♪ Turning into something
I'll never forget ♪

588
00:38:50,210 --> 00:38:52,140
♪ In the long journey of life ♪

589
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:56,670
♪ The meaning of encounters
can never be defined ♪

590
00:38:54,070 --> 00:38:54,950
Your hand.

591
00:38:57,300 --> 00:39:04,460
♪ The story isn't over yet,
and tears are not the only part of it ♪

592
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:02,110
From now on,

593
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:04,090
I'll entrust Wan to you.

594
00:39:05,380 --> 00:39:10,730
♪ Turn love into a secret,
hidden deep inside ♪

595
00:39:05,470 --> 00:39:08,470
Remember, I'm not too old to walk yet.

596
00:39:08,550 --> 00:39:09,630
If

597
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:11,200
you dare let my Wan

598
00:39:10,930 --> 00:39:14,690
♪ Collecting moments
as we pass by each other ♪

599
00:39:11,200 --> 00:39:13,030
suffer even the slightest grievance,

600
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:15,680
I'll show up in front of you
anytime, anywhere

601
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:21,510
♪ To look back on when I grow old ♪

602
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,520
to teach you a lesson.

603
00:39:18,920 --> 00:39:21,570
Great Aunt, if that's your only reason
for returning to the capital,

604
00:39:21,570 --> 00:39:22,930
I'm afraid there won't be
such an opportunity.

605
00:39:22,340 --> 00:39:27,200
♪ Turn love into a secret,
hidden deep inside ♪

606
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,320
Wan! Wan!

607
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:31,390
♪ If you unveil the mystery ♪

608
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:37,610
♪ And walk through this journey with me ♪

609
00:39:40,300 --> 00:39:48,300
♪ That would be the best ending for love ♪

610
00:39:52,100 --> 00:39:52,890
Go ahead.

611
00:39:57,820 --> 00:39:59,940
The late Emperor's edict:

612
00:40:00,190 --> 00:40:02,110
My young son, Yan Sui,

613
00:40:02,130 --> 00:40:04,080
is naturally kind and generous,

614
00:40:04,110 --> 00:40:05,890
filial and sincere.

615
00:40:06,010 --> 00:40:08,220
He now succeeds to the throne,

616
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:09,930
rules over the realm,

617
00:40:10,270 --> 00:40:12,360
bestowed with the mandate of Heaven,

618
00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:14,510
assumes the imperial position
in this world,

619
00:40:14,510 --> 00:40:17,360
hereby proclaimed to all under heaven.

620
00:40:18,240 --> 00:40:19,860
Prince Rui, Yan Chi,

621
00:40:19,880 --> 00:40:21,360
is of noble character,

622
00:40:21,470 --> 00:40:23,130
wise and filial,

623
00:40:23,240 --> 00:40:25,680
quelled chaos and laid down arms,

624
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:28,470
defended the palace
and saved the late Emperor,

625
00:40:28,470 --> 00:40:30,150
and achieved great merits.

626
00:40:30,150 --> 00:40:30,990
He's hereby

627
00:40:30,990 --> 00:40:32,820
appointed as Regent,

628
00:40:32,970 --> 00:40:34,410
to assist the successor,

629
00:40:34,430 --> 00:40:35,950
united in purpose,

630
00:40:36,200 --> 00:40:38,240
following the path of past sages.

631
00:40:43,470 --> 00:40:44,240
Rise.

632
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:46,000
Thank you, Your Majesty.

633
00:41:15,030 --> 00:41:16,150
When you return to Jingzhou,

634
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:17,590
take good care of Grandma,

635
00:41:17,590 --> 00:41:19,470
and take even better care of yourself.

636
00:41:19,470 --> 00:41:22,350
Forget all those past events and people.

637
00:41:22,950 --> 00:41:24,120
Don't worry.

638
00:41:24,240 --> 00:41:25,890
I won't make things hard for myself.

639
00:41:25,890 --> 00:41:28,490
Yan Ze lost his life
due to his own inner demons.

640
00:41:28,630 --> 00:41:29,840
I no longer owe him anything.

641
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:31,530
I just need some time

642
00:41:31,590 --> 00:41:33,650
to figure out what kind of life I want.

643
00:41:33,870 --> 00:41:35,930
That's the best way to think about it.

644
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:38,150
Could you help me deliver something?

645
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:39,030
To whom?

646
00:41:43,070 --> 00:41:46,070
If you don't come down soon,
the boat's going to leave.

647
00:41:50,430 --> 00:41:51,070
Coming!

648
00:41:52,610 --> 00:41:53,530
Coming!

649
00:41:58,660 --> 00:41:59,340
Ning.

650
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:00,110
I'm here.

651
00:42:00,380 --> 00:42:01,780
So this is what she meant.

652
00:42:03,680 --> 00:42:05,780
I've always seen Yan Li
as a sister since childhood.

653
00:42:05,780 --> 00:42:07,110
You must treat him well.

654
00:42:07,550 --> 00:42:08,150
Sister?

655
00:42:08,720 --> 00:42:09,920
You can slap his face,

656
00:42:10,190 --> 00:42:11,320
but don't bruise it,

657
00:42:11,580 --> 00:42:12,820
or he'll cry.

658
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:14,950
Don't worry, Chi.

659
00:42:15,240 --> 00:42:17,240
Just for the sake of his pretty face,

660
00:42:17,590 --> 00:42:18,680
I'll go easy on him.

661
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:20,490
While he's still young and beautiful,

662
00:42:20,490 --> 00:42:21,680
hurry up and get married,

663
00:42:21,680 --> 00:42:23,810
or you'll miss his prime and regret it.

664
00:42:27,680 --> 00:42:29,030
Is there something on my face?

665
00:42:29,030 --> 00:42:30,510
Little Wan'er is right.

666
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:32,480
I shouldn't miss your prime.

667
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:35,470
Don't worry, my beauty is timeless.

668
00:42:36,790 --> 00:42:38,680
So do you want to get married soon or not?

669
00:42:38,680 --> 00:42:39,480
Of course I do.

670
00:42:40,240 --> 00:42:41,440
We'll be leaving now.

671
00:42:57,070 --> 00:42:58,130
Have you set a date?

672
00:42:59,550 --> 00:43:00,260
-Yes.
-No.

673
00:43:03,840 --> 00:43:05,440
Princess Wan, please don't mock us.

674
00:43:05,440 --> 00:43:07,190
You've always been so wishy-washy.

675
00:43:07,190 --> 00:43:08,990
When asked about marriage,
you flatly deny it.

676
00:43:08,990 --> 00:43:10,500
Do you believe
I'll send you to guard the border?

677
00:43:10,500 --> 00:43:11,500
No, please don't.

678
00:43:13,100 --> 00:43:13,980
The date is set.

679
00:43:14,030 --> 00:43:15,960
Just wait for the wedding banquet.

680
00:43:17,450 --> 00:43:20,290
Setting sail!

681
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:26,470
♪ Having walked alone through
wind and rain for years ♪

682
00:43:26,490 --> 00:43:29,660
♪ Never having encountered this love ♪

683
00:43:30,580 --> 00:43:34,620
♪ Until you came to my world ♪

684
00:43:34,650 --> 00:43:37,880
♪ And wrote our destined bond ♪

685
00:43:38,620 --> 00:43:42,130
♪ The sunshine you gave me ♪

686
00:43:42,420 --> 00:43:46,000
♪ Painted pictures of the future ♪

687
00:43:46,710 --> 00:43:50,690
♪ Only when I drew near to you
did I realize ♪

688
00:43:50,720 --> 00:43:53,780
♪ This love was already deep and endless ♪

689
00:44:00,280 --> 00:44:01,680
This is the first year of Decheng.

690
00:44:01,680 --> 00:44:03,360
To follow heaven's mandate

691
00:44:03,360 --> 00:44:04,560
and serve the common people,

692
00:44:04,560 --> 00:44:05,870
I hereby reform the Criminal Code.

693
00:44:05,870 --> 00:44:08,320
There's a new article
added to the Criminal Code:

694
00:44:08,320 --> 00:44:10,430
Anyone who kills due to emotional reasons

695
00:44:10,430 --> 00:44:12,510
and anyone who beats to death
a cohabitant,

696
00:44:12,510 --> 00:44:14,030
whether married or not,

697
00:44:14,030 --> 00:44:15,880
shall have their punishment
increased by one level.

698
00:44:15,880 --> 00:44:17,760
Anyone who deliberately
kills a cohabitant,

699
00:44:17,760 --> 00:44:19,090
whether married or not,

700
00:44:19,210 --> 00:44:20,510
shall be sentenced to death

701
00:44:20,510 --> 00:44:22,040
with immediate execution.

702
00:44:23,110 --> 00:44:24,840
Anyone who molests a young girl

703
00:44:24,950 --> 00:44:26,280
shall be exiled 3,000 li

704
00:44:26,400 --> 00:44:27,950
to a remote, harsh province.

705
00:44:27,950 --> 00:44:29,430
Anyone who rapes a young girl

706
00:44:29,430 --> 00:44:30,560
shall be strangled.

707
00:44:32,710 --> 00:44:34,130
Anyone who,
under the pretext of medical treatment,

708
00:44:34,130 --> 00:44:35,880
removes organs from a living person

709
00:44:35,880 --> 00:44:37,030
or causing injury

710
00:44:37,050 --> 00:44:38,030
shall be strangled.

711
00:44:38,030 --> 00:44:39,200
Those who commit murder

712
00:44:39,200 --> 00:44:40,260
shall be beheaded immediately—

713
00:44:40,260 --> 00:44:42,120
the crime is beyond forgiveness.

714
00:44:43,370 --> 00:44:45,450
Anyone who violates the law

715
00:44:45,470 --> 00:44:47,070
while resisting unjust harm

716
00:44:47,320 --> 00:44:49,260
shall receive reduced punishment
based on circumstances,

717
00:44:49,260 --> 00:44:51,660
so the righteous will not suffer unjustly.

718
00:44:52,330 --> 00:44:54,760
Anyone who gathers crowds
to promote evil occult practices

719
00:44:54,760 --> 00:44:56,070
or spreads rumors to deceive the public,

720
00:44:56,070 --> 00:44:57,660
shall, for minor offenses,
be relocated for three years

721
00:44:57,660 --> 00:45:00,490
and detained for reeducation
until they understand proper principles.

722
00:45:00,040 --> 00:45:03,390
[Fortune-Telling]

723
00:45:00,590 --> 00:45:02,920
Anyone who causes physical harm or injury
to another person through beating

724
00:45:02,920 --> 00:45:04,110
shall be exiled for 3,000 li.

725
00:45:04,110 --> 00:45:06,200
Anyone who murders or rapes
women or children

726
00:45:06,200 --> 00:45:07,320
shall be beheaded immediately.

727
00:45:07,320 --> 00:45:09,590
The new code has received
His Majesty's approval

728
00:45:09,590 --> 00:45:10,880
and shall take effect immediately.

729
00:45:10,880 --> 00:45:12,470
All previously concluded cases

730
00:45:12,470 --> 00:45:14,760
shall be reviewed and punished
according to the new, stricter standards.

731
00:45:14,760 --> 00:45:16,150
Great!

732
00:45:16,150 --> 00:45:18,030
Great! Excellent!

733
00:45:18,860 --> 00:45:20,180
[Zhaoxue Hall]

734
00:45:55,920 --> 00:45:56,920
Bring the medicine box.

735
00:45:56,920 --> 00:45:57,360
Yes.

736
00:46:03,110 --> 00:46:04,070
A new case?

737
00:46:04,830 --> 00:46:05,360
Let's go.

738
00:46:17,150 --> 00:46:21,160
[No Injustice in the World]

